<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmed - Food Paradise</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-white min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
<div class="bg-zinc-800 border border-amber-400 max-w-xl relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-8 w-full text-center">
    <div class="absolute top-0 h-2 right-0 left-0 bg-amber-400"></div>
    <div class="bg-orange-500/10 p-10 rounded-full text-4xl animate-bounce md:text-5xl border border-orange-500/30 w-20 h-20 flex justify-center items-center mx-auto">🎉</div>
    <h2 class="text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase">Order
    <span class="text-amber-400 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase">confirmed!</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-zinc-300 font-light text-lg">Thanks, <span class="text-amber-400 text-xl font-bold"><%= name %></span> your order is successfully booked</p>
    <div class="bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-xl p-4 mb-8 text-left space-y-2 mt-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Status</span>
            <span class="text-green-400 font-bold tracking-tight text-lg">Pending Confirmation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="delivery flex items-center justify-between w-full">
            <span>Delivery</span>
            <span>Tiffin Reaches Readlly</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/menu" class="block w-full bg-amber-500 text-black p-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-black hover:text-amber-500 hover:border hover:border-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.4)]">Back to menu</a>
    <a href="/" class="block w-full bg-amber-500 text-black p-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-black hover:text-amber-500 hover:border hover:border-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.4)] mt-3">Back to Home</a>
    <a href="/admin/orders" class="block w-full bg-amber-500 text-black p-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-black hover:text-amber-500 hover:border hover:border-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.4)] mt-3">Dashboard of Paradise</a>

</div>

